of your presence on that occasiona large company
expectedfront seats reserved for the ladies; and
Hugh laughed at his hideous joke.
He's a desperate hard case, I suppose; I should
like wonderfully to see himyou don't know where
they keep him, I suppose?
Don't know? returned Hugh; maybe I don'tif
I don't know, who does?that's it. See here, my
